      <b data-is-speakable>From Private Helicopters To Concierge Doctors, Inequality Is A 'Big Business'</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Nelson Schwartz, author of <em>The Velvet Rope Economy,</em> says special privileges for the super-rich are dividing America: "The result is less sympathy, less empathy and a sort of a harder-edge society."</b>
